column5: :take  daughter to aunts for school at 6:30am{usual time} :drive  pick-up with bicycle and fishing equipment to work :throw bike and gently place fishing gear in work truck{5 ton} :drive to leslie spit and unload bike and gear :bike out to promising locations on spit and catch huge pike ,,photo,,,release ,,,,repeat!! :return to 5 ton truck ,reload , proceed to job appointment for 2:oopm  desperate times ,,, desperate measures !!!
